Panamerican Games 2007 (Rio de Janeiro, Brazil)

Venues:
Centro Esportivo Miécimo da Silva
Centro de Futebol Zico (CFZ)
Estádio João Havelange (a.k.a. "Engenhão")
Estádio do Maracanã

Men´s Tournament

(for U-20 teams; South American teams will play with their U-17 teams; three over-age players
are allowed for each team)

